                    <history>
                        <origin>
                            The document was written on <origDate when="1937-07-30" when-custom="1929-09-23" calendar="ethiopian">
                                23 Ḥamle 1929 E.C. = 30 July 1937 A.C.</origDate>, possibly by order of 
                            <persName ref="PRS4938HabtaMa"><roleName type="title">Daǧǧāč</roleName> Habta Māryām</persName>.
                        </origin>
                        <provenance>According to <bibl><ptr target="bm:Triulzi2006Orality"/><citedRange unit="page">51</citedRange></bibl>,
                            it is not clear, whether the manuscript was confiscated or handed over to the Italian authorities. The document was sent
                            together with an Italian translation (cf. <ref target="#accMat1"/>) in a letter by <persName ref="PRS15333Fasulo"/> 
                            from <placeName ref="LOC4964Naqamt"/> to <persName ref="PRS7170Moreno"/> in
                            <placeName ref="LOC3495Jimma"/>.   
                             Later it was entrusted by <persName ref="PRS7170Moreno"/> to <persName ref="PRS3182ContiRo"/>.</provenance>
                    </history>
